The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to the cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of matrix-space models, which are often used in the field of neural networks for computer vision (cs.CV) and computational neuroscience (cs.NE).
